      "source": [
        "# 🎨 DiffuSVG: Complete Experimental Pipeline\n",
        "\n",
        "**Prompt → Diffusion → Image → VLM → SVG**\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook runs the complete DiffuSVG pipeline and generates real experimental results.\n",
        "\n",
        "## What this notebook does:\n",
        "1. **Phase 1**: Fine-tune SDXL with LoRA for vector-style image generation\n",
        "2. **Phase 2**: Use VLM (Claude/GPT-4V) to convert images to SVG code\n",
        "3. **Phase 3**: Iterative refinement with visual feedback\n",
        "4. **Evaluation**: Compute CLIP Score, DINO Score, validity metrics\n",
        "\n",
        "**Estimated Runtime**: ~2-4 hours on T4 GPU (free Colab)\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
      ]
    },
